Description: Lip sherd of Attic pottery Siana or lip-cup; lip offset inside; interior: reserved band at rim, glazed black below; exterior: black band at lip, reserved below; inscription cut on interior.
Bibliographic references: Bernand 1970 / Le Delta égyptien d'après les textes grecs, i: les confins libyques (pl. 22.2.5)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GA.1693)
